        <item>
            <title>日本环球影城「咚奇刚国度」12 月 11 日开幕，过山车、主题餐厅、精品店抢先睇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/12/donkey-kong-country/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=donkey-kong-country</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/12/donkey-kong-country/hottopic/walk/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:00:14 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩乐好去处]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Super Nintendo World]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[咚奇刚国度]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1274367</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">任天堂董事宫本茂宣布，日本大阪环球影城「Super Nintendo World」（Super Nintendo World）将在今年 12 月 11 日推出全新扩展园区「咚奇刚国度」（Donkey Kong Country）。园区内设有机动游戏、主题餐厅及精品店。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_36216"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HUbSpOcunTg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲「咚奇刚国度」（Donkey Kong Country）将在今年 12 月 11 日开幕（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「咚奇刚国度」以熟悉的《咚奇刚》游戏元素为主题，贯穿丛林与黄金神庙等经典场景。游客可以透过新增的咚奇刚与狄狄刚专属互动手环，配合手机应用程式参与到多种沉浸式体验当中，而旧款手环也适用于新园区。在园区内，不只可以探索隐藏在各处的互动装置，还能收集游戏印章，体验包括音乐节奏游戏「康加鼓节奏击鼓」等特色活动，让游客仿如亲身参与到咚奇刚的动作世界中。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274371 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-5-694x376.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-5-694x376.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274378 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-10-694x374.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="374" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-10-694x374.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-10-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274372 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-6-694x373.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-6-694x373.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-6-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲贯穿丛林与黄金神庙（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274375 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-8-694x372.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-8-694x372.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-8-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲游客可以透过新增的咚奇刚与狄狄刚专属互动手环（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274376 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-9-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-9-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-9-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配合手机应用程式参与到多种沉浸式体验当中（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274374 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-7-694x374.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="374" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-7-694x374.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-7-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲音乐节奏游戏「康加鼓节奏击鼓」（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「咚奇刚国度」设有「咚奇刚的疯狂矿车」，是一款以矿车为主题的过山车游乐设施，游客可随著矿车飞驰穿越丛林，体验不可预测的惊险转折。过山车的身高要求为 122 厘米以上（有监护人陪同时可放宽至 107 厘米），而整段游玩时间约为两分钟。过山车的面貌并未在宣传片中完全揭露，留待游客亲身探索。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274380 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-11-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-11-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-11-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274381 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-12-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-12-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-12-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「咚奇刚的疯狂矿车」的面貌并未在宣传片中完全揭露，留待游客亲身探索（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了刺激的游乐设施，「咚奇刚国度」亦设有专属餐饮与购物选择，例如餐厅「Jungle Beat Shake」提供以香蕉为主题的特制饮品和甜品。园区内还开设了「Funky Kong&#8217;s Fly and Buy」精品店，供应一系列咚奇刚及狄狄刚周边商品。游客还有机会与咚奇刚本人会面及合照。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274382 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-13-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-13-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-13-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274383 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-14-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-14-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-14-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274384 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-15-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-15-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-15-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲餐厅「Jungle Beat Shake」提供以香蕉为主题的特制饮品和甜品（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274387 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-17-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-17-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-17-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274388 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-18-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-18-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-18-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「Funky Kong&#8217;s Fly and Buy」精品店供应一系列咚奇刚及狄狄刚周边商品（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274386 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-16-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-16-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-16-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲游客还有机会与咚奇刚本人会面及合照（图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
